Package: rsnplots
Title: Theme utilities for 'ggplot2' and 'vegabrite' in the Refugee Solidarity Network style
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Kevin", family = "Cole", email = "kevin@rsn.ngo", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides theme utilities to standardize plots created in both "ggplot2" and "vegabrite" (an R wrapper for the Vega-Lite API), in line with Refugee Solidarity Network (RSN) style guides. This package builds on the Urban Institute's [urbnthemes] package.
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    scales,
    extrafont,
    ggrepel,
    systemfonts,
    vegabrite,
    dplyr
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.1
